Kernel, firmware, devices and hacks for Raspberry Pi

This script will run the following SlackBuilds:
   raspi-boot
   raspi-hacks
   kernel_raspi
   kernel-modules-raspi
   installer (if DOINSTALLER=yes)
   kernel-source-raspi (if DOSOURCE=yes)

Before running this script, you must download some files:
to take care of this run
  sh ./get_needed_files.sh

- - -

This is a fork of https://github.com/idlemoor/raspi-slackbuild

updated for the latest upstream development kernel, 3.6.11,
with BFQ patches added.
